#
#   This .gitignore is LOCKED DOWN.
#
#   DO NOT add entries here without EXPLICIT user (Smooth511) approval.
#   DO NOT ignore evidence/, investigation/, logs/, chat-logs/, exports/,
#       core/, mk2-phantom/, or ANY directory that holds operational data.
#
#   These directories contain forensic evidence, investigation logs, and
#   operational records.  Ignoring them = destroying evidence = instant
#   trust revocation.
#
#   If you think something should be ignored, raise it with the user.
#   If you're an agent and you're "cleaning up" — this is NOT the place.
#
#   Last reviewed: 2026-03-23 by ClaudeMKII (lockdown compliance pass)
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── PROTECTED DIRECTORIES — NEVER IGNORE THESE ───────────────────────────
# evidence/        → forensic evidence (NEVER ignore)
# investigation/   → analysis reports (NEVER ignore)
# logs/            → operational logs (NEVER ignore, except parsed JSON)
# chat-logs/       → recovered chat data (NEVER ignore)
# core/            → framework definitions (NEVER ignore)
# mk2-phantom/     → protected vault (NEVER ignore)
# exports/         → GitHub data exports (NEVER ignore)
# assets/          → screenshots, visual evidence (NEVER ignore)

# ── Parsed EVTX output (too large for repo) ──────────────────────────────
logs/*.json
!logs/.gitkeep

# ── Python ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.Python
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
dist/
build/
.pytest_cache/

# ── Virtual environments ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
venv/
env/
.env

# ── IDE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/settings.json
.vscode/launch.json
.vscode/tasks.json
.vscode/extensions.json
.vscode/*.code-workspace
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── OS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Temp files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.tmp
*.bak
